1. Every html element is embedded into a box which has 4 layers (content, padding, border, margin).
h1{
border-style:solid; (dashed,dotted,solid,(inset,outset-3D View))
border-width:5px;
border-color:red;
border-left-color:green;
border-bottom-color:orange;

}
<h1>Box Model</h1>


NOTE: Border shorthand notation =>
border:5px solid blue;
i.e. border: border-width border-style border-color;
